<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Walk Boulder</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/style.css">
</head>
<body>



  <div class="container">
    <h1>WALK BOULDER</h1>
    <p>WalkBoulder is a free web-mapping hand application that can be used by any Boulder local using modes of transportation other than their own. WalkBoulder is free and for residents who want a more walkable city. Unlike Google Maps, WalkBoulder is interactive and tailored specifically toward Boulder residents, with reviews and suggestions from verified locals.</p>

    <input type="text" placeholder="Find Trails" class="search-bar">

    <hr>


    <div class="trail">
      <div class="trail-info">
        <h2></h2>
        <p></p>
      </div>
      <div class="trail-image">[Image Placeholder]</div>
    </div>
    <hr>

  </div>


<button class="btn btn-primary mt-3" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#review_modal">
                Write Review
            </button> 

<div class ="modal" id="review_modal" tabindex="-1">
  <div class = "modal-dialog">
    <div class = "modal-content">
      <div class = "modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title">Write a Review</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
          <form>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="trail_name" class="form-label">Trail Name</label>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="event_name" class="form-label">Rating</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="event_name" placeholder="share your thoughts on this trail" required>
                    </div>
                    
          </form>
      </div>
              <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" onclick="saveReview()" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                Post
              </button>
            </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>